data.description: Rare 4 Bed/2 Bath THREE CAR garage ON the POND!  PRICED TO SELL by this motivated family, this is a 2020 year built D.R Horton Del Ray floor plan with 2032 square feet of comfy living space in this popular gated community of Entrada.  Plus, the mortgage is assumable at a low interest rate.    NO FLOOD zone & some of the LOWEST HOA fees you'll find in Southwest FL, which includes Quantum Fiber Internet and MyQ App for gates/amenities access.  STAINLESS STEEL kitchen appliances & GRANITE countertops for your beautiful kitchen.  Take notice of the stylish tile in the shower of the master bathroom.  A well sized screened-in Lanai to relax creating serenity of your POND view & rare species of birds and wildlife. So many reasons to enjoy this well-lived in home.    Resort style amenities await you at the Village of Entrada! Beautiful beach entry pool with lap lanes, splash pad & playground for the kids, fitness center, bocce ball, pickle-ball/tennis court, food truck nights, and a clubhouse used for various clubs & activities. This home is conveniently located to shopping, movies, restaurants, and downtown Ft. Myers!  You've arrived to your perfect home, welcome.
